                  </hi>. I am first officer of the <hi rend="italic">Madagascar</hi>—he commander's name is Charles Grange Weller, and the shipper's is John Henry Vivian.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> A man said, "If you take it on shore, lay it against the wall, I will give you 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.;" he took the handkerchief off my neck, and tied it round me.</p>
